    {
      "para_id": "Q001987.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninibgal , the compassionate lady , who loves votive offerings , who listens to prayers and supplications , her shining mother , Enlil-bani , the shepherd , who makes everything abundant for Nibru , the farmer of Urim’s plentiful barley , who purifies all divine powers of Eridug , the beloved en - priest of Unug , the powerful king , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse choosen in the heart by Inana , built her beloved temple ."
    }
  ],
